 User Stories!
 
 As a user, I can create quizzes, because I want to test people.
 As a user, I can make quizzes private, because I want to limit access.
 As a user, I can share a link to a quiz, because I want people to take my quizzes.
 As a user, I can view others' public quizzes on the homepage, because I am interested in taking quizzes.
 As a user with a link, I can take a quiz, because I got a link from a user.
 As a user, I can see the results, because I want to know my score.
 As a user, I can share a link to my results, because I want to show people my scores.
